e","tid":2152863,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T08:23:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/UYH4WSPYKBG7TG55N6YF5RQZWI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FUYH4WSPYKBG7TG55N6YF5RQZWI%2F&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf5riIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=46cdc7e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FUYH4WSPYKBG7TG55N6YF5RQZWI%2F&h=8ad28e36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/UYH4WSPYKBG7TG55N6YF5RQZWI/</a><br />\n<br />\n政權瘋狂打壓《蘋果日報》後，《蘋果》今天有三版全版廣告。<strong><span class=\"red\">A1頭版嘅阿布泰國生活百貨</span></strong>，除咗提醒大家「酒好飲 報好睇 切勿酒後駕駛」之外，仲hashtag「蘋果一定撐落去」。賣口罩嘅<strong><span class=\"red\">同舟Unite Mask</span></strong>就買咗A9全版，白底黑字「同舟共濟」，睇番佢facebook亦貼咗個廣告，hashtag寫明「香港人加油」同「撐蘋果」；另外A11全版廣告就係網購平台<strong><span class=\"red\">啱你買ArmuBuy。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n另外，都有唔少廣告商，落四分一版廣告撐蘋果撐香港。其中A12版嘅<strong><span class=\"red\">M.E. Pro 企業管理顧問</span></strong>，就白底黑字叫大家「見字飲水」，又hashtag「我哋真係好＿鍾意香港」同埋「香港人撐住」。A13版有署名「香港市民」落咗句「一日一蘋果」，A18版仲有<strong><span class=\"red\">班鳩成人用品專門店</span></strong>落嘅廣告，語帶雙關咁話「香港人，夠硬！」<br />\n<br />\n有廣告商更似乎打算「連載」廣告，喺A18版落咗四分一版嘅<strong><span class=\"red\"><a href=\"http://網購平台HisTrend.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%B6%B2%E8%B3%BC%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0HisTrend.HK&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf5riIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=6e8759c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">網購平台HisTrend.HK</a></span></strong>，黑底白字印咗個「我」字，八方見到時心中都有問號，睇番佢facebook專頁解釋，就話「一個廣告，唔代表一日就完成；正如支持《蘋果日報》一樣，唔係買一日就完；如果你唔明，你買多幾日你就明。」睇來大家要買多幾日《蘋果》先睇得明個廣告喇。<br />\n<br />\n亦有廣告商選擇落空白廣告，包括A13版嘅<strong><span class=\"red\">日希移民</span></strong>同埋A17版嘅<strong><span class=\"red\">玄機閣梁善行師傅</span></strong>。至於噚日先落完空白廣告嘅<strong><span class=\"red\">訂機票網上平台「又飛啦！Flyagain.la」</span></strong>，似乎覺得效果唔錯，今日喺A13版嘅廣告唔再空白，而係寫住「感謝！一日增加2萬新粉絲。呢度賣廣告，效益宏大！」<br />\n<br />\nC5版仲有個分類小廣告，細細一格除咗「抱緊自由」四隻字，仲有林夕同羅冠聰改詞版《約定》嘅歌詞，同埋同「我願榮光歸香港」同音嘅「5201314」。<br />\n<br />\n撐《蘋果》嘅唔只廣告商，仲有唔少政界人士。其中民主黨立法會議員許智峯就喺facebook貼出今日出版嘅《蘋果日報》，留言話「這是一場持久戰，不是一日可以抵擋強大力量。我們還要繼續撐住珍貴的媒體，捍衞新聞自由，捍衞第四權，好讓香港不同的聲音可以繼續發聲。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T08:36:01.000Z","msg":"聽日可能係個「願」定？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d820076b985240afe6c94c0a9f4216d774ee6c9","tid":2152863,"uid":131622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T08:37:13.000Z","msg":"（緊急召集）富山報紙攤仲剩大量蘋果需要大家幫手掃！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2152852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2152852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7870c58fc38efa840762f61a772252e64beaebbb","tid":2152863,"uid":130140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T08:38:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote></blockquote>聽日可能係個「願」<span class=\"red\">字</span>？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5590ecfe9dd09c51fb6db122ad5aff89f95631ad","tid":2152863,"uid":358691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T08:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b80341235007293a5badaf51926c863b33cc670","tid":2152863,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4cf9115f3e154c728ff6c00fb6220601d652b59","tid":2152863,"uid":20558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0b302d1e52a1f5e98d42b1db6d872b15b42d9d3a","tid":2152863,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"461e5eff0bf7a1c0d6298b5a12bbb61a94901ef7","tid":2152863,"uid":219010,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T08:26:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有廣告商更似乎打算「連載」廣告，<a href=\"http://喺A18版落咗四分一版嘅網購平台HisTrend.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%96%BAA18%E7%89%88%E8%90%BD%E5%92%97%E5%9B%9B%E5%88%86%E4%B8%80%E7%89%88%E5%98%85%E7%B6%B2%E8%B3%BC%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0HisTrend.HK&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf5riIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=fb80e14c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">喺A18版落咗四分一版嘅網購平台HisTrend.HK</a>，黑底白字印咗個「我」字，八方見到時心中都有問號，睇番佢facebook專頁解釋，就話「一個廣告，唔代表一日就完成；正如支持《蘋果日報》一樣，唔係買一日就完；如果你唔明，你買多幾日你就明。」睇來大家要買多幾日《蘋果》先睇得明個廣告喇。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n估係 W DLLM 689<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T08:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T08:31:43.000Z","msg":"原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我仲以為係我睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:23:41.000Z","msg":"「連載」廣告!! <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁可能要買足成個星期蘋果先睇得哂佢個廣告~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73e61fd0c966c71aec500f633498edb8cfb6ebc","tid":2152863,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T11:42:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4733fd4a7d008bb5d42060531141123bb794c8a6","tid":2152863,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7870c58fc38efa840762f61a772252e64beaebbb","tid":2152863,"uid":130140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T08:38:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote></blockquote>聽日可能係個「願」<span class=\"red\"